[[Spectrum painter|https://github.com/polygon/spectrum_painter]]
converts images to digital signal processing IQ streams
that can be viewed in a
[[spectrogram|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spectrogram]].
Transmitting SDR's like [[HackRF|http://greatscottgadgets.com/hackrf/]]
and [[bladeRF|http://hackaday.com/2013/02/02/bladerf-your-next-software-defined-radio/]]
have software
that enables you to directly load up
and play out a file over the radio interface.

